Fix Tier 4 daily case not opening (missing from seed + broken image URLs)

Root cause: Tier 4 case was manually added to the dev DB but never added
to the DAILY_CASES seed array in seed.ts, so it was absent from production.
The dev DB copy also had broken /@fs/home/runner/workspace/... image URLs.

Fix:
- Added Tier 4 to DAILY_CASES in artifacts/api-server/src/seed.ts with all
  6 items and correct /api/assets/... image URLs
- Server restart triggered seedDailyCases() which updated the dev DB record
  with proper paths; next production deploy will seed it automatically

Pattern going forward: all daily cases must live in DAILY_CASES in seed.ts
